SUE: The visual says it all.

30:42.133 --> 30:44.667
That's not a healthy
freaking product.

30:44.733 --> 30:47.033
But the quality of what I buy

30:48.433 --> 30:50.467
is just outstanding.

30:50.533 --> 30:53.267
So it just hurts,
hurts, hurts, financially.

30:53.333 --> 30:55.633
But, you know
I put a lot of me.

30:55.700 --> 30:57.933
Kavik is me.
Ya know, I am Kavik.

30:58.000 --> 30:59.133
Synonymous.

30:59.200 --> 31:01.667
But I take a lot of pride
in offering people

31:01.733 --> 31:03.600
the best of the best
when they're out here.

