But I mean every single
little bit of this
is lost, lost, lost.

31:13.733 --> 31:15.700
I mean,
besides the disgusto factor,

31:16.667 --> 31:18.900
um, I mean

31:18.967 --> 31:21.633
it's an incredible amount
of revenue.

31:21.700 --> 31:24.167
How do you put a price tag
on the caribou?

31:24.233 --> 31:26.333
Or the fish
that I bartered for.

31:27.700 --> 31:30.100
Hard to put a value on that.

31:32.400 --> 31:33.600
You know,
if there's anything close,

